{"tid":2075796,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部稱堅決反對任何利用病毒溯源問題搞污名化的做法","createTime":"2020-06-23T05:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T05:48:04.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"811c5f951cc0da9bfae8520656b1b6a30f504ce9","tid":2075796,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:36:41.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普日前出席競選集會期間，表示可以將新型冠狀病毒稱為「Kung flu」，被指涉及種族歧視。在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅說，世衛與國際社會明確反對將病毒與特定國家及地區關聯，中方堅決反對任何利用病毒溯源問題搞污名化的做法，亦注意到美國國內亦有不少有識之士，公開譴責利用疫情搞污名化，發表種族主義的做法。<br />\n<br />\n對於美國國務卿蓬佩奧在哥本哈根民主高峰會上指責中國，趙立堅批評這位美國政客的言論違背基本事實，違背國際關係基本準則，中方堅決反對，認為只會進一步暴露其根深蒂固的冷戰思維與意識形態偏見，奉勸對方糾正錯誤，停止散播政治病毒，多做有利中美合作，而不是破壞合作的事。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533458-20200622.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533458-20200622.htm&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7kaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=f5f898fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533458-20200622.htm&h=423515bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533458-20200622.htm</a>"},{"pid":"33404f958a10c8a8aa7d201472a3836223b68c5f","tid":2075796,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:43:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B22Qp3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB22Qp3Y.jpg&h=78f2e4fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"162b275fc0a2dca5bc6902a525c6aadc12d2d829","tid":2075796,"uid":31058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:47:14.000Z","msg":"其實依加中共嘅外交政策到底係點？ 正常都會搵下盟友，但佢地就好似癲狗咁，見人就咬，到底係咩手段黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309d1a577bceb304ca9ede24a13408f158f488c6","tid":2075796,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:48:04.000Z","msg":"非洲豬瘟唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" 